
📘 Specs & Design

🔗 RFC 3875 – CGI/1.1 Specification
	https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc3875.html
	Defines CGI environment variables, stdin/stdout behavior, and response formatting.

💡 Practical Guides
	🔗 Linux fork() + execve() + pipe() tutorial
	Explains how to wire up CGI scripts with UNIX syscalls.

🔗 CGI and Environment Variables
	https://www6.uniovi.es/~antonio/ncsa_httpd/cgi/env.html
	https://www.cgi101.com/book/ch3/text.html
